snippet: The International Space Station accepted its first American shipment in more than half a year on Wednesday, receiving Christmas presents and groceries for the resident astronauts.
abstract: American space station receives cargo of Christmas presents and groceries from supply ship Cygnus, first American shipment in over half a year.
lead_paragraph: The International Space Station accepted its first American shipment in more than half a year on Wednesday, receiving Christmas presents and groceries for the resident astronauts.
